==English==

===Proper noun===
'''[[sleeping|Sleeping]] [[beauty|Beauty]]'''

# The main character in a fairy tale of the same name, who is in unbroken slumber under a magical spell, awaiting the kiss of a prince. The originally tale was titled ''La Belle au Bois dormant'' by [[w:Charles Perrault|Charles Perrault]].

